reviews.text:
I couldn't wait and had to taste this recipe immediately after mixing. The dull but overpowering LB Pink Lemonade was all I could taste, leaving me worried that steeping wouldn't be enough to fix how flat it tasted. &#xD;
&#xD;
&#xD;
Surprise surprise though, after just 36 hours of steeping the difference is huge. The LB Pink Lemonade mellowed out allowing everything else to shine through big and bold. I'm shocked at how much it came to life.&#xD;
&#xD;
&#xD;
I'm guilty of loving extra sweet commercial juices, so I bumped the Super Sweet up to 1%. It works pretty well here in my opinion. &#xD;
   &#xD;
&#xD;
All in all this could be the holy grail for lovers of the original. It really does taste just like the commercial version. I wouldn't be surprised if it turned out to be identical to Twist's own recipe.
